  <brief_title>Diurnal Variation in Hypertensive Stroke Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of the Effects of Amlodipine and Losartan on Blood Pressure and Diurnal Variation in Hypertensive Stroke Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
