  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study was conducted to evaluate and compare the effectiveness of Amodipin® (amlodipine
      camsylate) with that of Cozaar® (losartan potassium) in hypertensive patients with an acute
      ischemic stroke by measuring their 24-hour ambulatory BP (ABP).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
